# supergemma4-unc — model definition for the Local Model sandbox
#
# Do NOT add a TEMPLATE directive here. v2 ships a neutral chat template baked
# into the GGUF specifically to fix the older routing bug where simple prompts
# drifted into coding/tool-call mode. Let Ollama use the embedded template.
FROM hf.co/Jiunsong/supergemma4-26b-uncensored-gguf-v2

# Ollama defaults num_ctx to a few thousand tokens regardless of what the model
# supports, and silently truncates. Set it explicitly or the agent layer later
# will misbehave.
#
# Start at 32K (safe on a 24 GB 4090), confirm stability, then bump to 65536.
# If you OOM at higher context, prefer flash attention + KV-cache quantization
# (see setup/setup.ps1) over dropping context. The constraint here is
# VRAM/context, never tok/s.
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768
